title: PML-N’s Syed Imran Ahmed Shah wins NA-141 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) candidate Syed Imran Ahmed Shah has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-141 Sahiwal-I by securing 1,18,240 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Rana Amir Shehzad Tahir, who bagged 1,07,056 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 49.83 percent.
